    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i've just run out. like everything i ever had to say, everything i ever wanted to create... it's just gone. there's no more color left, just this grey emptiness. i look at my studio and it just feels like a graveyard of things that don't matter anymore. i don't even know why i'm still trying to wake up every morning.",
